break for electric car buyers, which stalled Tesla sales and caused overall demand for battery-powered cars to crash<br />\n<br />\nUS electric car maker Tesla is &shy;prepared to reduce its Hong Kong operations if the government fails to give residents incentives to buy battery-powered cars in its &shy;upcoming budget, a source close to the company told the Post.<br />\n<br />\nThe source said Tesla, led by billionaire entrepreneur Elon Musk, had written to Chief Executive Carrie Lam Cheng Yuet-ngor asking her to rethink last year&rsquo;s &shy;removal of a full registration tax waiver on electric cars for private use. The move resulted in buyers paying as much as 80 per cent more for high-end models.<br />\n<br />\nWith the tax waiver capped at HK$97,500 from April 1 last year, sales of electric cars nosedived. Only 99 new cars were registered from April to December last year, compared with 2,078 in the same period the year before."},{"pid":"3191abdef842c965649be445c07c78429ea55cf8","tid":550680,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"960a093d85bdd8b8f0f78d68060928d24a972c2d","tid":550680,"uid":143572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:00:35.000Z","msg":"政府唔ON9, tesla以外既代理扭計。<br />\n唔知做左幾多利益輸送先可以加電動車稅。<br />\n今年可能冇著數, 咪搞9你班代理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"真係好撚仆街<br />\n把口就要人環保，下年仲話收垃圾稅<br />\n但實際上所有政策都係為錢"},{"pid":"eea7731e382912f9b7e0886a2a5e98ff566eb5d6","tid":550680,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:49:57.000Z","msg":"查下波叔有冇囤積TESLA好過啦"},{"pid":"a05996c0c8f62821c7364376dbbbf8952ff16e14","tid":550680,"uid":47824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"屌 原本屋企人係打算買tesla<br />\n因為買左車位<br />\n去到最後搞到無得買"},{"pid":"255a3ad071c98f3c24232a1ef3299e2101018eec","tid":550680,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a05996c0c8f62821c7364376dbbbf8952ff16e14","tid":550680,"uid":478